this is where app icons is contained

ex: icon.png || icon.svg



SVG Icon (better quality)

For SVG, you need the package:
flutter_svg

Add in pubspec.yaml:

dependencies:
  flutter_svg: ^2.0.0

(flutter pub get)

Then use:

import 'package:flutter_svg/flutter_svg.dart';

SvgPicture.asset('assets/icons/coffee.svg')


